    <h1>ℹ️About Us</h1><br>

    <b>Welcome to our English Vocabulary learning website!</b><br><br>

    <p>Our mission is to help students, beginners, and English learners improve their vocabulary in a simple and effective way. We provide easy-to-understand English words with Urdu meanings, pronunciation, example sentences, synonyms, antonyms, and practice quizzes.</p><br>

    <b class="paragraph">We believe that learning a few new words every day can make a big difference in your English speaking, writing, reading, and listening skills.</b><br><br>

    <p class="para1">Our goal is to make English learning simple, enjoyable, and accessible for everyone.</p><br>

    <p class="para1">Thank you for visiting our website. We hope our content helps you achieve your English learning goals.</p><br>

    <b>Happy Learning!</b><br>
